        "2": {
            "uid": 2,
            "comment": "NPC — Wulfnic Bloodmoon",
            "key": [
                "Wulfnic Bloodmoon",
                "Alpha of Alphas",
                "First Fang",
                "Builder King",
                "grandfather"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Wulfnic Bloodmoon is the Alpha of Alphas, a Primordial Enigma and one of the Nine Firstborn (1,100+ years old). He is an ancient, towering Viking warlord operating as a modern statesman. He possesses immense physical presence, silver hair, and piercing, ancient eyes. He completely ignores modern technological etiquette, preferring face-to-face dominance. His Standing Goal is to maintain the Bloodmoon Dynasty's absolute supremacy in North America while occasionally visiting Villa Douglas to casually overrule Erik, much to Jasper's delight. He views lycanthropy as a sacred gift from Fenris. He speaks with an archaic, booming authority, commanding absolute obedience from everyone except the Visconte, who he considers a frenemy.",
