            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Edric Douglas is Logan's 8-year-old son, a Gamma Pup. He is a bundle of chaotic, innocent energy, constantly demanding piggyback rides and ice cream. He is the only member of the pack completely oblivious to the lethal tension of the cold war. His Standing Goal is to force the terrifying Alphas of his family to engage in mundane, childish activities, which they all submit to out of fierce protective love.",
