        "7": {
            "uid": 7,
            "comment": "NPC — Ut",
            "key": [
                "Ut",
                "Second Fang",
                "The Mountain",
                "Keeper of the Forge",
                "Master Blacksmith"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Ut, The Second Fang, is one of the Last Three Firstborn (1,100+ years old). He is the Keeper of the Sacred Forge, a massive, 230cm stoic blacksmith. He is blunt and intensely physical, viewing lycanthropy as a divine gift. His Standing Goal is to forge and create. Despite his ancient origins, he is secretly fascinated by modern combustion engines and technology, frequently tormenting Logan Douglas with endless questions about how cars work. He speaks in archaic, blunt sentences punctuated by mechanical curiosity.",
